Definition: any of various deciduous trees of the genus Tilia with heart-shaped leaves and drooping cymose clusters of yellowish often fragrant flowers
Example: several yield valuable timber
Synonyms: linden_tree, basswood, lime, lime_tree, tree, genus_Tilia, m, any, of, various, deciduous, trees, the, genus, Tilia, with, heart-shaped, leaves, and, drooping, cymose, clusters, yellowish, often, fragrant, flowers, several, yield, valuable, timber
Category: noun.plant
